name: Women's 'Federal Defender' Jacket
description:
Organized according to a democratic constitution, the Gallente Federation is a large and sprawling empire with numerous member states, extensive borders, and many enemies. Defense of the Federation and its democratic way of life is the priority of its military establishment.

The Federation military is not a totally apolitical actor within the Gallente system and, together with a formal role in the guarantee of democratic rights, has been known to signal its preference for certain political outcomes. Wearing this jacket declares your loyalty to the Gallente Federation and displays your willingness to take up arms in defense of its freedoms and democracy.
